You may just be discontent with yourself, you may hope to lift your miserable
self up if only you can be special or do something great. This view is flawed
your real issue is not achieving some arbitrary thing but rather not accepting
yourself. Further, it is dangerous to treat one's life as en-route to some
summit. If you work hard and suffer for a better life, you're gambling with the
